                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I took the prisoner and property in charge. I had the silver weighed - the value as old silver is above 8 l.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I throw myself entirely on the mercy of the Court.</p>
